features: ELEGANT VINTAGE STYLE: The side table combines natural wood grain finish boards with thickened Roman column table legs to emphasize its carving's side elegant lines and great craftsmanship in details, which showcases a vintage glam style and creates a stylish and luxurious vibe, making it an elegant and timeless eye-catcher to fit perfectly with almost all other furniture items. It is not just a side table, but a decoration artwork, that adds an elegant touch to your living room or bedroom.

ROBUST BUILD: Our end table is crafted from high-grade MDF engineered wood and heavy-duty metal, ensuring it's sturdiness and durability. The waterproof thickened tabletop provides excellent stability, allowing the side table to bear up to 150 lbs, which is more than sufficient for your needs. The thickened metal legs of the side table ensure that it is stable and does not shake. 3 Adjustable footpads are designed for leveling or uneven, and protect your tile and wood floors from scratches.

MULTIFUNCTIONAL END TABLE: The height of the end table is designed to match most sofas and beds, making it an ideal choice as a sofa side table, bedside table, nightstand, end table, or accent table. It is suitable for use in a bedroom, living room, office, small spaces, or any other area. The bedside table features an attractive design that combines industrial, contemporary, and retro styles, making the nightstand compatible with any home decor and furniture.

SPACIOUS STORAGE: The round end table overall size is 18.1”L x 18.1”W x 23.6”H; The 3 tiers storage shelves structure makes it a larger storage space. Teacups, decorations, books, phones, drinks, and other items are within arm's reach and help keep the living area away from clutter. The wooden grain desktop is waterproof and very easy to clean. With high-quality materials and excellent craftsmanship, the accent table can withstand extended use without fear of wear and tear.

EASY to ASSEMBLY: This round end table has been checked and is well-packed before shipping. You don't need to worry about assembly, the living room side table comes with detailed installation instructions, parts and accessories are labeled with numbers, and precise holes make installation accurate and fast. 1 person can assemble in about 15 minutes. If you have any questions before or after your purchase, you can always email us, and we always reply within 24 hours.
